WEBVTT

00:18.500 --> 00:19.800
我的命在你手里
My life is in your hands.

00:20.100 --> 00:21.600
LJ和莎拉怎样了?
How's LJ? how's Sara?

00:21.900 --> 00:23.100
她死了 迈克
She's dead, Michael.

00:23.300 --> 00:24.300
我骗了你
I lied to you.

00:24.300 --> 00:25.390
索菲亚·鲁果
Sofia Lugo

00:25.400 --> 00:27.290
我是詹姆斯·惠斯勒的女友
I'm James Whistler's girlfriend.

00:27.300 --> 00:30.490
我要你从这越狱 斯科菲尔德先生
You are breaking out of this prison, mr. Scofield,

00:30.500 --> 00:32.000
并且带上我
And you're taking me with you.

00:32.000 --> 00:33.000
再过四天
Four more days.

00:33.200 --> 00:34.700
我就会从这出去了
If I'm out of here by then,

00:34.800 --> 00:36.190
我能行的
I can still do it.

00:36.200 --> 00:38.090
在过去的两天内
There ve been two escape attempts

00:38.100 --> 00:39.600
出现了两次试图越狱行为
In the past two days.

00:39.700 --> 00:42.100
和索纳说再见吧 斯科菲尔德先生
Say good-bye to Sona, mr. Scofield.

01:11.900 --> 01:13.300
到了 我们单独谈下
Right there. Leave us.

01:14.600 --> 01:17.200
我的前任 艾斯伽米上校
My predecessor, colonel Escamilla,

01:17.800 --> 01:19.090
工作干得不够好
Wasn't an effective leader.

01:19.100 --> 01:20.500
因此被替换了
He's been replaced.

01:20.600 --> 01:22.200
我是萨瓦拉狱官
I am general Zavala.

01:22.500 --> 01:23.200
坐吧
Sit.

01:24.200 --> 01:25.100
要喝水么?
A drink of water?

01:29.100 --> 01:31.190
尊敬的狱官阁下 这次越狱事件
With all due respect, general, I had nothing to do

01:31.200 --> 01:32.600
跟我无关
With what happened here today.

01:32.800 --> 01:35.400
我的调查向来细致入微
I always conduct a thorough investigation,

01:35.400 --> 01:37.700
但这里有太多的疑问要解决
And there are too many unanswered questions here.

01:38.500 --> 01:41.300
我的任务就是去把这些都搞清楚
It is my job to find those answers.

01:41.300 --> 01:43.200
如果你帮我 那我也会帮你
If you help me do my job, I'll help you.

01:44.100 --> 01:45.000
那架直升机
The helicopters.

01:46.200 --> 01:48.400
不是你所能够弄到的
You alone couldn't be responsible for that.

01:48.400 --> 01:48.990
那直升机
You certainly weren't

01:49.000 --> 01:50.790
-应该与你无关 是吧? -是的
Flying a helicopter, were you? no.

01:50.800 --> 01:51.890
-和谁有关? -我不知道
Who was? I don't know.

01:51.900 --> 01:53.300
-但你知道是谁派来的? -不知道
But you know who sent them. no.

01:55.000 --> 01:56.400
我还是要建议
Again, be advised

01:56.700 --> 01:59.200
你还是说实话的好
Telling the truth is in your best interest.

01:59.700 --> 02:00.400
我说的就是实话
I am.

02:06.200 --> 02:07.600
我们去走走
Let's go for a walk.

02:07.800 --> 02:09.590
我知道你内心的恐惧
I understand your fears,

02:09.600 --> 02:11.390
但是巴拿马政府不允许这样的事发生
But the republic of panama cannot allow

02:11.400 --> 02:14.100
如果你愿意说的话
This sort of activity. if you wish to talk,

02:14.400 --> 02:15.400
现在正是时候
Now is the time.

02:16.700 --> 02:17.400
我会的
I would

02:18.700 --> 02:19.890
可我已经全说了
If there wasanything left

02:19.900 --> 02:21.990
那我别无选择了
Then you give me no choice.

02:22.000 --> 02:22.800
过来这边
This way.

02:25.800 --> 02:27.000
情况不妙
This isn't good.

02:27.600 --> 02:29.100
他们要把他给蒸喽
They're putting him in the hot box.

02:30.000 --> 02:31.900
这会很不好受的
Things are gonna get much harder for you.

02:33.300 --> 02:34.400
你无路可走
There's no way to win.

02:34.400 --> 02:36.100
只有合作
You must cooperate.

02:37.200 --> 02:38.090
承认自己的行为
Confess to this escape

02:38.100 --> 02:39.800
并且承担该受的惩罚
And face your punishment by law,

02:40.500 --> 02:41.790
否则就等着更严重的后果
Or face a far greater punishment

02:41.800 --> 02:43.300
在太阳下好好想想
In the panama sun.

02:43.300 --> 02:44.700
你自己定夺吧
It's up to you.

02:48.100 --> 02:49.300
他完了
He's done.

02:49.900 --> 02:51.200
全完了
He's finished.

