希望我弟弟没事
I hope my brother's all right.

03:56.500 --> 03:57.200
很痛么?
Does it hurt?

03:57.400 --> 03:58.000
没事
It's fine.

03:58.800 --> 04:00.000
我要去监狱那边
I'm gonna get to the prison.

04:00.600 --> 04:02.500
我在候车室看到了新闻
I was watching the news in the waiting room.

04:02.800 --> 04:04.900
他们确定了几具尸体的身份 但是
They identified a few bodies, but

04:05.000 --> 04:05.790
不是他们
It wasn't them.

04:05.800 --> 04:06.890
到那就清楚了
I'll find out when I get there.

04:06.900 --> 04:07.700
你去么?
You want to come?

04:07.800 --> 04:09.000
我不知道
I don't, I don't know.

04:09.300 --> 04:10.490
在发生这么多事之后
After everything that's happened,

04:10.500 --> 04:11.800
我都不知道怎么办了
I don't know what to think anymore.

04:12.100 --> 04:13.400
有什么好多想的?
What more is there to think about?

04:13.400 --> 04:14.990
詹姆斯 对任何事都有解释
James has an answer for everything,

04:15.000 --> 04:16.600
但是没有一个解释有意义
And nothing ever makes sense.

04:16.600 --> 04:17.690
你该停止问问题
You need to stop asking questions

04:17.700 --> 04:18.890
而去看看事实
And just look at the facts.

04:18.900 --> 04:20.900
我愿意相信他所说的一切
I wanted to believe everything he was saying,

04:21.000 --> 04:23.600
而且我还是想要他出来
And I still want him to get out.

04:24.100 --> 04:25.200
我也希望他能出来
I want him out as well.

04:26.000 --> 04:28.200
相信我 我每天都在竭尽全力
Trust me, I've been working on this every single day.

04:29.500 --> 04:31.800
林肯 对你所做的一切 我真的很感激
Lincoln, I really appreciate everything you have done.

04:32.800 --> 04:34.300
你救了我的命
You saved my life.

04:34.600 --> 04:36.400
你不必这样帮我的
You didn't have to help me like that.

04:36.800 --> 04:37.700
不 应该的
Yeah. I did.

04:44.300 --> 04:45.200
上车
Get in the car.

04:45.400 --> 04:46.200
快点
Come on

04:57.000 --> 04:59.300
我到哪 你就到哪
Everywhere I go, there you are.

05:01.200 --> 05:02.400
回家去 索菲亚
Go home, Sofia.

05:17.500 --> 05:19.800
我很想开车冲出大门 阿历克斯
Part of me wanted to drive right past this gate, Alex.

05:21.100 --> 05:22.400
你不该在这里
You don't deserve to be here.

05:23.600 --> 05:27.900
事实上 如果你考虑到所有的事 我是应得的
Actually, if you take all things into consideration I do.

05:34.500 --> 05:34.990
谢谢
Thank you.

05:35.000 --> 05:35.900
等下
Wait.

05:40.600 --> 05:41.500
不用
Don't.

05:43.100 --> 05:44.290
我父亲在矿井里
My father worked in a mine

05:44.300 --> 05:45.500
工作了30年
For 30 years,

05:46.500 --> 05:48.100
每天去工作他都带上这
He took this into work with him every day.

05:49.800 --> 05:51.400
保他平安 直至退休
Kept him safe till the day he retired.

05:52.700 --> 05:53.700
之后他把这给了我
Then he gave it to me.

05:57.700 --> 05:59.000
我不能收下
I can't take this.

06:00.100 --> 06:01.300
等你出来后再还我
Give it back when you get out.

06:05.500 --> 06:06.590
保重 阿历克斯
Take care of yourself, Alex.

06:06.600 --> 06:07.900
嗯
Yeah.

06:45.400 --> 06:47.400
怎么 你没胆量自己亲自动手?
What? you ain't got the guts to do it yourself?

06:48.600 --> 06:50.800
听着 在我改变主意前 给我闭嘴
This is for you, so shut up before I change my mind.

06:51.300 --> 06:52.590
昨天之后 你也许在怀疑
After yesterday, you may be doubting

06:52.600 --> 06:55.400
我完成协议的能力
My ability to make good on our agreement.

06:55.800 --> 06:57.100
但你们的命仍然还有用
I need to keep you motivated.

06:57.600 --> 06:58.600
你有1分钟时间
You have one minute.

07:06.900 --> 07:07.600
爸爸
Dad

07:09.700 --> 07:12.000
LJ 谢天谢地 你还活着
LJ. LJ, thank you're alive.

07:20.100 --> 07:20.790
不 别做傻事了
No, forget about it.

07:20.800 --> 07:21.890
你无能为力的
There's nothing to do.

07:21.900 --> 07:22.690
总会有些漏洞之类的
There's always something

07:22.700 --> 07:23.500
爸爸
Dad

07:23.700 --> 07:24.690
这些家伙无处不在
These guys are thorough

07:24.700 --> 07:27.100
他们处处跟踪你 相信我
They follow you everywhere. Trust me.

07:30.600 --> 07:31.900
那婊子是个疯子 什么都干的出
There's nothing that bitch is crazy.

07:32.500 --> 07:34.100
他割了莎拉的头
She cut Sara's head off.

07:34.800 --> 07:35.900
她不能把这事办砸了 当时我在场
She cannot lost that offer. I was there.

07:36.300 --> 07:38.000
我虽被蒙了眼 但是我听到了
I clozed my eyes but I heard.

07:38.400 --> 07:39.400
听我说
Listen to me.

07:39.700 --> 07:41.900
我不会失去你的 知道吗?
I could not let that happen without you, all right?

07:42.200 --> 07:43.500
下次你看到我
The next time you see me,

07:43.600 --> 07:45.200
一定要注意看着我
Don'take your eyes off me.

07:45.200 --> 07:46.190
我会告诉你怎么做
I'll tell you what to do.

07:46.200 --> 07:47.100
知道么?
All right?

07:47.400 --> 07:48.300
时间到了
Minute's up.

07:49.600 --> 07:50.800
你叔叔和我
Me and your uncle,

07:51.100 --> 07:52.700
我们知道怎么做
We know what we're doing.

07:52.700 --> 07:54.000
我们会救你出来
We're gonna get you out of this.

07:55.500 --> 07:56.190
我爱你
I love you.

07:56.200 --> 07:57.300
我爱你 爸爸
I love you, dad.

08:25.600 --> 08:27.300
似乎情况不妙啊
Looks like things didn't go so well.

08:27.600 --> 08:28.400
你应该已经出去了的
You should be gone.

08:29.200 --> 08:30.200
你也是啊
So should you.

08:31.000 --> 08:31.800
发生什么事了?
What happened?

08:34.100 --> 08:35.000
还没结束呢
It's still happening.

08:36.000 --> 08:38.500
对于迈克 我很遗憾 不过我们还是有办法的
I feel bad for Michael, but we have a way without him.

08:38.800 --> 08:39.800
你该歇歇了
You should get some rest.

08:40.300 --> 08:41.300
怎么出去?
What's the way?

08:42.100 --> 08:44.900
我会歇歇的 会的 会的 等我出去后
I'll rest. I'll rest. I'll rest when I'm out.

08:45.200 --> 08:46.100
我一定会带上你的
I won't go without you.

08:46.700 --> 08:47.700
相信我
You have my word.

08:48.100 --> 08:49.000
去歇歇吧
Now get some rest.

08:59.300 --> 09:01.400
看到斯科菲尔德在那蒸笼里了吧?
You see Scofield out in that redneck sauna?

09:01.800 --> 09:03.990
看看他还有没有办法从里面出来
Let's see if he has the oo to get out of that one.

09:04.000 --> 09:05.400
你也有份 是吧?
You were in on it, right?

09:06.000 --> 09:08.100
我发现你们在勒齐的周围晃动
I see you guys lurking around Lechero.

09:08.200 --> 09:10.100
斯科菲尔德肯定想好了逃离的计划
Scofield's gotta he a plan to escape.

09:10.200 --> 09:11.700
如果真有 那么我全然不知
If so, I know none of it.

09:12.200 --> 09:13.700
没错 我想你也不知道
Yeah, I bet you don't.

09:15.400 --> 09:15.900
天呐
Whoa.

09:16.100 --> 09:18.600
鸡尾酒喝多了 吐得的到处都是啊
Too many cocktails out on the lido deck.

09:20.500 --> 09:22.000
麻烦来了
Here comes trouble.

09:23.500 --> 09:26.400
库拉达 把这儿清理了
Ser Criada, clean it up.

09:26.600 --> 09:27.800
是啊 是该清理一下
Yeah, I'll get right on that.

09:28.100 --> 09:29.100
你听到我说的了吗
You heard what I said.

09:29.200 --> 09:30.190
我说把这儿清理了
I told you to do something.

09:30.200 --> 09:31.890
现在就去做 清理脏东西
Now do it. cleaning up chunks

09:31.900 --> 09:33.490
已经不再是我的工作了
Ain't in my job description anymore.

09:33.500 --> 09:34.790
哦 情况变了
Oh, things changed.

09:34.800 --> 09:36.700
听着 你现在听我们的指挥
You see, you answer to us now.

09:36.700 --> 09:38.200
听着 猛男 你吓唬不了我
Hey, caveman, you don't scare me.

09:38.700 --> 09:40.100
去吓唬别人好了
Go bug someone else.

10:22.400 --> 10:23.600
你在这里干什么?
What are you doing here?

10:23.700 --> 10:24.900
我来送个重要的东西
I have a special delivery.

10:26.100 --> 10:27.600
我需要你把这个火速带进去
I need to get it in real quick.

10:28.200 --> 10:29.000
出多少?
How much?

10:29.700 --> 10:30.600
我出一万
I gave you ten grand.

10:30.800 --> 10:32.400
一万是上次的价 这个给多少
Ten grand was the last one. how much for this one?

10:34.000 --> 10:34.800
免费
No grand.

10:35.100 --> 10:35.690
那不了 谢谢
Then no thanks.

10:35.700 --> 10:36.600
不 别 别急
No, no no

10:38.300 --> 10:39.900
我觉得你应该
I think you might

10:41.400 --> 10:44.100
再好好想想
want to reconsider

10:49.300 --> 10:51.200
把水拿给那个囚犯
Take this water to the prisoner.

10:51.800 --> 10:52.900
为什么我去? 他根本不配喝水
Why should i? he doesn't deserve it.

10:55.700 --> 10:56.400
我来吧
I'll do it.

11:11.500 --> 11:12.100
兄弟
Hi, brother.

11:12.900 --> 11:14.000
还记得我吗?
Remember me?

11:14.900 --> 11:16.400
这样做没有用
This isn't gonna work.

11:17.100 --> 11:18.090
快 把这个喝下去
Come on, papi, drink this.

11:18.100 --> 11:20.900
我不能让LJ出事 明白吗?
Don't leanything happen to LJ, okay?

11:21.300 --> 11:24.300
我明白 他的情况比你好多了
It's okay. he's doing much better than you.

11:24.400 --> 11:26.700
快 喝下这杯 你需要的
Come on. drink this. you need it.

11:37.600 --> 11:38.700
莎拉的事情我很抱歉
I'm sorry about Sara.

11:41.900 --> 11:44.200
下次我试着溜进监狱更深的地方 好吗?
I'm gonna try to sneak more into the prison next time, okay?

11:44.600 --> 11:45.600
我要你放弃
I want you to quit.

11:46.500 --> 11:47.100
我做不到
I can't.

11:47.600 --> 11:50.100
-我们都需要适可而止 -不 迈克
We all have to quit sometime. no, Michael.

11:50.600 --> 11:53.190
你现在困在这个鸡笼中 你现在正是需要帮助的时刻
You're here in a chicken coop you need all the help you can get.

11:53.200 --> 11:55.190
不需要你来帮 走吧 不要回头
Don't need your help. just go, and don't look back.

11:55.200 --> 11:56.790
-你为我做了那么多 我不会丢下你 -走
Not after everything you've done for me.

11:56.800 --> 11:59.600
离开这 快走吧
Just leave, go.

12:13.600 --> 12:14.590
这么说你昨天试着搭乘直升机
So you tried to catch a flight

12:14.600 --> 12:15.900
从这里逃出去?
Out of here yesterday?

12:16.000 --> 12:17.200
只能这样 没有办法
I had to do wh I had to do.

12:17.500 --> 12:19.000
没错 但是你现在回到我们的交易中
Yeah, but you went back on our deal.

12:19.600 --> 12:20.990
我只是在帮助我自己
I was saving my own ass.

12:21.000 --> 12:22.290
我相信你还记得计划
I'm sure you're familiar with the strategy.

12:22.300 --> 12:23.300
现在 你听好了
Now, you watch it.

12:23.400 --> 12:24.300
在这里我还是老大
I'm still boss here.

12:24.700 --> 12:25.800
谁还在乎老大是谁?
Who cares about who's boss?

12:26.400 --> 12:27.090
你还想从这里出去吗?
Do you want to get out of here,

12:27.100 --> 12:28.300
或者你想在这里喋喋不休?
Or do you want to keep talking about it?

12:31.900 --> 12:32.600
没事
It's okay.

12:32.700 --> 12:33.900
我们只是需要把这块撑起来
We just need to brace it.

12:35.300 --> 12:37.000
不 我们需要结构工程师
No. we need the engineer.

12:37.800 --> 12:38.500
把它挪开
Move it.

12:39.800 --> 12:41.200
萨米回来之前 我们赶快离开这里
Let's get out of here before Sammy gets back.

12:58.300 --> 13:01.600
阴凉处华氏98度 笼子里边125度
98 degrees in the shade, 125 in the box.

13:01.600 --> 13:03.490
让我们进去 找个空调房间
Let's go inside. we'll have a chat

13:03.500 --> 13:04.900
好好谈谈
In the air conditioning.

13:05.200 --> 13:06.500
明天会更热
Tomorrow is going to be hotter,

13:06.900 --> 13:08.600
后天 就像小火炉一样
The next day, even hotter.

13:08.600 --> 13:10.800
大后天 你就会成一具死尸
The day after that, you'll be dead.

13:11.400 --> 13:12.500
你不明白
You don't understand.

13:13.700 --> 13:15.000
如果我认为你能帮我
If I thought you could help me

13:16.800 --> 13:17.700
我能够
I can.

13:18.400 --> 13:19.790
你不明白我在这个省
You're unaware of the influence

13:19.800 --> 13:21.300
的庞大关系网
I have in this province.

13:21.300 --> 13:25.300
你希望我是你的盟友而不是敌人 不是吗?
You'd rather I be your ally than your enemy, wouldn't you?

13:25.300 --> 13:26.700
你不了解这些人
You don't know these people.

13:27.400 --> 13:29.700
我们无法阻止他们 至少你不能
We can't stop them not you,

13:30.400 --> 13:31.700
也不是我
Not me.

13:33.800 --> 13:37.090
曾经有个人 一个大毒枭
There was a man a drug kingpin

13:37.100 --> 13:38.900
巴拿马最有权势的人
The most powerful man in panama.

13:39.300 --> 13:42.190
一个冷血的杀手 身后有一只由暴徒
A ruthless killer with an army of thugs

13:42.200 --> 13:43.800
小偷组成的军队
